"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-news-olympic-cross-country-team-standings-after-second-rotation-of-riders-865876\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Strong performances in theParis Olympiccross-country phase are keeping the huge crowds entertained as Britain continues to hold the top team spot.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 102, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9207023117869787, \"rank\": 0.08610779871468618, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of the second rotation of team riders on Olympics cross-country day, Britain continues to hold the top spot, followed by France, then Japan.\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9207023117869787, \"rank\": 0.08610779871468618, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9035999229070306, \"rank\": 0.07955628275264559, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 293, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9849241115103051, \"rank\": 0.013720391066052441, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan's Yoshi Oiwa kept a cool head to deliver a clear round aboard the experienced MGH Grafton Street.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9849241115103051, \"rank\": 0.013720391066052441, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6020155261369017e-25, \"text\": \"Yoshi\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yotsuya_Kaidan\", \"score\": 0.994671424598866, \"rank\": 0.005357121225495462, \"text\": \"Oiwa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yotsuya_Kaidan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yotsuya_Kaidan\"}, {\"begin\": 387, \"end\": 390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts_General_Hospital\", \"score\": 0.9821746560570878, \"rank\": 0.01814885349862229, \"text\": \"MGH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts_General_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts_General_Hospital\"}, {\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grafton_Street\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grafton Street\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grafton_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grafton_Street\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair came home inside the time to finish on their 25.50 dressage.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yoshi and \\\"Squirrel\\\" have only been a partnership for three months, butPippa Funnell- who rode the 16-year-old gelding to victory at Burghley in 2019 - has been guiding the partnership.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6020155261369017e-25, \"text\": \"Yoshi\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Squirrel\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.4418019313353713e-12, \"text\": \"Squirrel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Squirrel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Squirrel\"}, {\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burghley_Horse_Trials\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.922786483489541e-30, \"text\": \"Burghley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burghley_Horse_Trials\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burghley_Horse_Trials\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's just an amazing horse,\\\" said Yoshi, who described his Olympic cross-country round as \\\"amazing\\\".\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6020155261369017e-25, \"text\": \"Yoshi\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoshi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a narrow track where you are galloping so the spectators are very close, there are a lot of people which I did not expect so much.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a beautiful round all the way round with everyone watching and cheering us.\\\"\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Frenchman Stephane Landois added 2.8 time-penalties to his 24.4 dressage with Chaman Dumontceau.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chaman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.687136944498425e-13, \"text\": \"Chaman\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chaman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chaman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephane said the 12-year-old gelding concentrated well throughout the course, stuck to the plan and \\\"did exactly what he needed to do\\\".\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is so much atmosphere and the crowd is so loud,\\\" he said \\\"My horse was a little taken aback so I really had to try hard to keep him concentrated and on track because he's not used to the crowds like this.\\\"\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke Johnstone could not hide his delight when he finished the Olympic cross-country with a clear jumping round aboard Menlo Park, adding 4.8 time-penalties to their 30.5 dressage.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarke_Johnstone\", \"score\": 0.9999543861659902, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clarke Johnstone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarke_Johnstone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarke_Johnstone\"}, {\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menlo_Park_station\", \"score\": 0.9995017386880729, \"rank\": 0.00045015401661198075, \"text\": \"Menlo Park\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menlo_Park_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menlo_Park_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not very often fist pump, but I was pretty excited at the finish,\\\" said Clarke.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just such a buzz about it.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue and weather is incredible, and I am proud to be a Kiwi, proud to be on the team, and really proud of my horse.\\\"\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9999937470320177, \"rank\": 5.626416033417538e-06, \"text\": \"Kiwi\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke said he \\\"could not fault\\\" 14-year-old Menlo Park.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menlo_Park_station\", \"score\": 0.9995017386880729, \"rank\": 0.00045015401661198075, \"text\": \"Menlo Park\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menlo_Park_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menlo_Park_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He left the start box and jumped every fence how I wanted.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was just on the job.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had no idea how he was going to cope with the crowds being so loud and so close to the fence and if anything, it helped me,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He just felt so motivated all the way around the course.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even towards the end of the course when I was asking him for a bit of extra effort he was really giving it to me.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's always a good jumper, and really reliable on his lines, but he honestly just skipped around and gave me a dream ride.\\\"\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"End of day update:Following the conclusion of the Olympic cross-country, Yoshi and MGH Grafton Street are individual fifth going into the 